  <div class="container-fluid">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-4">
                <img class="bucket_list" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534267209097-770ea651eb71?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=e8a5d71650e0751f2449ceac03c4e888&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1044&q=80">
                <p>Whether you’re hiking, camping or doing some yoga, Backcountry has all the activewear, accessories and gear you’ll need for ANY size adventure this summer.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-4">
                <img class="bucket_list" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534265084078-f9fc03b3f725?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=981795767d1d529f254fc7b3fbd4cd3e&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1650&q=80">
